      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this specimen, from the flawless exterior luster to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a standard of meticulous care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically superb and aesthetically indistinguishable from its original showroom state, this unit offers a definitive driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast. We invite you to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard used inventory, offering investment-grade quality and uncompromising performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
