    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior still has that new car vibe. It drives like a total dream and has been pampered since day one. I'm only letting it go because I'm moving, so I've priced it for a quick sale. Come take a look and fall in love! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 42900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
