      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. The S54 power unit features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS, delivering linear torque up to a soaring 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual remains tactile and precise, feeding a factory limited-slip differential with zero lash. This example boasts a reinforced subframe and original bushings in exceptional health. The factory finish retains its deep luster, while the Nappa leather interior shows no bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically synchronized, investment-grade driver's car.",
